1
00:00:23,450 --> 00:00:26,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure this is far enough?</font>

2
00:00:26,890 --> 00:00:31,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. I'll make the rest 
of the journey alone.</font>

3
00:00:31,900 --> 00:00:36,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, my destination 
is only accessible on foot.</font>

4
00:00:37,170 --> 00:00:39,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well. Take care.</font>

5
00:01:26,270 --> 00:01:33,320
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="33"><font face="Georgia"><font color="#9eccf8">Beyond Journey's End</font></font></font></b></font>

6
00:02:31,010 --> 00:02:35,010
<font face="Times New Roman" size="12"><b>{\an9}30 years after the death of Himmel the Hero,
in the Drachen region, located on the Northern Plateau</b></font>

7
00:02:48,860 --> 00:02:50,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This looks bad.</font>

8
00:02:51,150 --> 00:02:54,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The village was attacked by a dragon.</font>

9
00:02:54,490 --> 00:02:57,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They even have dragons 
on the Northern Plateau?</font>

10
00:02:57,250 --> 00:02:59,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This really is a dangerous place.</font>

11
00:03:00,090 --> 00:03:01,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It could be worse.</font>

12
00:03:01,810 --> 00:03:02,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

13
00:03:02,730 --> 00:03:06,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I traveled with Himmel, we were 
attacked by a flight of dragons.</font>

14
00:03:08,180 --> 00:03:10,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't even imagine a whole flight.</font>

15
00:03:10,690 --> 00:03:11,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's crazy.</font>

16
00:03:12,330 --> 00:03:17,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... do dragons not 
normally travel in flights?</font>

17
00:03:17,930 --> 00:03:20,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was this village attacked by a flight?</font>

18
00:03:20,340 --> 00:03:24,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. One moved in nearby.</font>

19
00:03:24,230 --> 00:03:26,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like you to slay them.</font>

20
00:03:27,130 --> 00:03:29,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Northern Plateau's 
normal is terrifying.</font>

21
00:03:29,590 --> 00:03:31,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's super crazy.</font>

22
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:52,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This village is done for.</font>

23
00:03:53,090 --> 00:03:54,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should move somewhere else.</font>

24
00:03:56,510 --> 00:04:01,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this is our home.</font>

25
00:04:02,140 --> 00:04:03,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be careful.</font>

26
00:04:03,040 --> 00:04:03,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?</font>

27
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll bring it to you now.</font>

28
00:04:07,990 --> 00:04:10,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's right, Ms. Frieren.</font>

29
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:13,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was a cruel thing to say.</font>

30
00:04:13,070 --> 00:04:15,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel sorry for the villagers.</font>

31
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:19,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you understand what it means 
to face a whole flight of dragons?</font>

32
00:04:19,550 --> 00:04:21,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no way we'll come away unscathed.</font>

33
00:04:22,130 --> 00:04:25,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We protect people's homes. 
Right, Frieren?</font>

34
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:28,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll depend on the pay.</font>

35
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:34,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our village is very poor. 
We have nothing to pay you with.</font>

36
00:04:34,080 --> 00:04:35,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have any grimoires?</font>

37
00:04:36,330 --> 00:04:40,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only one for a terribly 
useless spell that allows you</font>

38
00:04:40,630 --> 00:04:43,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to say tongue twisters without 
tripping over your words.</font>

39
00:04:43,970 --> 00:04:47,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That does sound useless.</font>

40
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:55,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Doesn't matter as long 
as it's a spell, huh?</font>

41
00:04:55,570 --> 00:04:58,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you know where 
the dragons came from?</font>

42
00:04:58,760 --> 00:05:01,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Somewhere in those woods.</font>

43
00:05:03,170 --> 00:05:05,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll search for traces of mana.</font>

44
00:05:06,230 --> 00:05:07,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We may be able to track them.</font>

45
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:34,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We continue straight here.</font>

46
00:05:34,880 --> 00:05:39,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been thinking this for a while now, 
but magic sure is amazing.</font>

47
00:05:39,590 --> 00:05:41,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's really convenient 
at times like these.</font>

48
00:05:42,310 --> 00:05:44,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep the praise coming.</font>

49
00:05:44,650 --> 00:05:50,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Stark, carelessly praising her isn't 
good for Ms. Frieren's development.</font>

50
00:05:50,490 --> 00:05:52,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess that's true.</font>

51
00:05:52,620 --> 00:05:55,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you two think I am?</font>

52
00:05:57,060 --> 00:06:00,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In any case, I can tell roughly 
which way they are. Let's go.</font>

53
00:06:35,490 --> 00:06:36,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There they are.</font>

54
00:06:36,790 --> 00:06:38,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a lot of dragons.</font>

55
00:06:38,630 --> 00:06:40,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But they're small ones.</font>

56
00:06:40,620 --> 00:06:43,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They won't be nearly as strong 
as that solar dragon.</font>

57
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:48,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That said, dragons are smart. 
Don't let them surround you.</font>

58
00:06:49,330 --> 00:06:52,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's draw them to one spot 
and take them down all at once.</font>

59
00:06:52,850 --> 00:06:55,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stark, keep them locked down.</font>

60
00:06:56,300 --> 00:06:58,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're an experienced 
dragon fighter, right?</font>

61
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:02,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Again? That's a tall order.</font>

62
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:08,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall we begin?</font>

63
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:10,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd better actually 
fire some spells this time.</font>

64
00:07:14,650 --> 00:07:17,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As long as you don't end up 
slaying them all first.</font>

65
00:08:26,380 --> 00:08:28,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was a ridiculously intense battle.</font>

66
00:08:29,450 --> 00:08:32,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a good thing this 
village has a church.</font>

67
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:36,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You even got your head 
chewed on during the fight.</font>

68
00:08:38,920 --> 00:08:40,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are you not in worse shape?</font>

69
00:08:44,900 --> 00:08:46,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know.</font>

70
00:08:46,720 --> 00:08:49,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's probably normal for warriors.</font>

71
00:08:49,260 --> 00:08:52,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eisen was fine after getting 
his head bitten, too.</font>

72
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:55,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, Mr. Eisen is definitely 
as far from normal as it gets.</font>

73
00:08:55,790 --> 00:08:57,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope you weren't waiting long.</font>

74
00:08:59,460 --> 00:09:03,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you. Here's your 
grimoire as payment.</font>

75
00:09:13,870 --> 00:09:20,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come to think of it, you almost always 
demand payment for helping people.</font>

76
00:09:20,820 --> 00:09:23,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because that's what Himmel did.</font>

77
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:24,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm surprised.</font>

78
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:29,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always assumed he was someone 
who helped others for free.</font>

79
00:09:30,060 --> 00:09:33,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know. I used to think the same thing.</font>

80
00:09:34,790 --> 00:09:36,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much.</font>

81
00:09:37,180 --> 00:09:44,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You deserve more, but as you can see, 
our village is poor.</font>

82
00:09:44,880 --> 00:09:47,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is all we have.</font>

83
00:09:49,410 --> 00:09:53,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't accept food from this village.</font>

84
00:09:56,700 --> 00:09:58,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that a grimoire?</font>

85
00:10:01,350 --> 00:10:05,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, it's a notebook we received from
 a traveling merchant some time ago,</font>

86
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:07,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but we have no use for it.</font>

87
00:10:17,510 --> 00:10:24,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Himmel, why do you demand payment 
nearly every time we help someone?</font>

88
00:10:25,060 --> 00:10:29,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If they pay us, 
they don't owe us anything.</font>

89
00:10:30,170 --> 00:10:32,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're the party of heroes.</font>

90
00:10:37,430 --> 00:10:44,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What we want is to help people, 
not words of gratitude.</font>

91
00:10:48,380 --> 00:10:55,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we make people indebted to us, 
we haven't really helped them.</font>

92
00:10:57,100 --> 00:11:02,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I even take ridiculous 
spells like this as payment.</font>

93
00:11:03,320 --> 00:11:04,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Frieren...</font>

94
00:11:06,460 --> 00:11:09,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to see if it really works later.</font>

95
00:11:09,770 --> 00:11:12,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the end, you just want spells.</font>

96
00:11:12,980 --> 00:11:17,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Couldn't you get a spell that 
prevents dragon bites instead?</font>

97
00:11:20,020 --> 00:11:23,030
<font face="Times New Roman">{\an7}<font color="#f7fffa">Episode 37: Himmel's Memoirs</font></font>

98
00:11:25,770 --> 00:11:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How's it look outside, Frieren?</font>

99
00:11:29,820 --> 00:11:32,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like we won't be able 
to head out for a while.</font>

100
00:11:33,430 --> 00:11:35,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's some terrible luck.</font>

101
00:11:35,640 --> 00:11:38,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe we're stuck here.</font>

102
00:11:38,310 --> 00:11:40,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so bored, I could die.</font>

103
00:11:40,500 --> 00:11:42,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's less the boredom 
and more the hangover.</font>

104
00:11:49,160 --> 00:11:51,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheer up, everyone.</font>

105
00:11:51,660 --> 00:11:55,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're on an adventure 
to defeat the Demon King.</font>

106
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:59,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We haven't been able to 
adventure for days now.</font>

107
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:03,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Adventures aren't just about 
strolling around in the great outdoors.</font>

108
00:12:03,940 --> 00:12:08,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sometimes, an adventure can just 
be a bunch of crappy days in a row.</font>

109
00:12:08,590 --> 00:12:11,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the only one calling it crappy.</font>

110
00:12:12,660 --> 00:12:14,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing, Himmel?</font>

111
00:12:15,350 --> 00:12:17,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is something the matter?</font>

112
00:12:20,130 --> 00:12:21,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No...</font>

113
00:12:22,290 --> 00:12:26,800
<font face="Times New Roman" size="12"><b>{\an9}30 years after the death of Himmel the Hero,
 by Lake Korridor, located on the Northern Plateau</b></font>

114
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:30,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been a week since 
we arrived in this city.</font>

115
00:12:30,060 --> 00:12:32,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The weather's as stormy as ever.</font>

116
00:12:40,890 --> 00:12:43,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will you be able to take 
the ferry out today?</font>

117
00:12:43,620 --> 00:12:45,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does it look like I can?</font>

118
00:12:53,700 --> 00:12:56,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My boat isn't a coffin, you know.</font>

119
00:12:58,590 --> 00:13:00,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose not.</font>

120
00:13:02,710 --> 00:13:07,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I gotta say, though. I'm surprised 
even lakes can get stormy.</font>

121
00:13:07,540 --> 00:13:11,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lake Korridor is the largest body 
of water in the northern lands.</font>

122
00:13:11,920 --> 00:13:14,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's larger than some inland seas.</font>

123
00:13:15,280 --> 00:13:18,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, we can hardly see the far shore.</font>

124
00:13:20,070 --> 00:13:24,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, large mountain ranges to the 
east and west disrupt air currents,</font>

125
00:13:24,560 --> 00:13:27,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">making this time of year 
hellishly stormy.</font>

126
00:13:27,930 --> 00:13:31,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not unusual for even large 
ships to sink in these storms.</font>

127
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:36,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With these winds, we can't use 
flying magic to cross, either.</font>

128
00:13:36,300 --> 00:13:39,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It would be difficult to fly across 
even on a clear day.</font>

129
00:13:40,150 --> 00:13:42,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The far shore is farther than you think.</font>

130
00:13:43,700 --> 00:13:48,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I might be able to make it, 
but you don't have enough mana.</font>

131
00:13:48,540 --> 00:13:51,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could we go around the lake?</font>

132
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:54,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That would be difficult, too.</font>

133
00:13:54,800 --> 00:13:56,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

134
00:13:56,850 --> 00:13:59,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The terrible weather is caused by...</font>

135
00:14:00,910 --> 00:14:02,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the mountain ranges to the east and west.</font>

136
00:14:03,170 --> 00:14:07,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Trying to cross a stormy mountain range 
without even a mountain pass...</font>

137
00:14:08,950 --> 00:14:10,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">would be suicide.</font>

138
00:14:11,150 --> 00:14:13,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Waiting here for a few months</font>

139
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:18,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is ultimately safer and quicker 
than trying to find a way around.</font>

140
00:14:19,020 --> 00:14:22,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fortunately, this is a fairly large 
port city and trading hub.</font>

141
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:25,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the perfect place to pass the time.</font>

142
00:15:08,100 --> 00:15:10,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We ended up waiting all winter.</font>

143
00:15:11,170 --> 00:15:12,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you take the ferry out today?</font>

144
00:15:12,820 --> 00:15:13,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

145
00:15:14,470 --> 00:15:16,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you pay, though?</font>

146
00:15:17,190 --> 00:15:21,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The storms may have passed, 
but it's still not a safe journey.</font>

147
00:15:22,110 --> 00:15:24,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I expect to be paid appropriately.</font>

148
00:15:27,390 --> 00:15:29,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not nearly enough.</font>

149
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:33,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is your fault for buying 
too many grimoires, Ms. Frieren.</font>

150
00:15:33,050 --> 00:15:34,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had a lot of time on my hands.</font>

151
00:15:35,750 --> 00:15:38,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, we can exchange favors.</font>

152
00:15:39,880 --> 00:15:41,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On an island just off shore,</font>

153
00:15:41,470 --> 00:15:46,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there's an abandoned monastery 
that's protected by a barrier.</font>

154
00:15:46,980 --> 00:15:51,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Himmel the Hero's memoirs 
are said to be there.</font>

155
00:15:52,180 --> 00:15:56,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Himmel the Hero saved this city 
during my grandfather's time.</font>

156
00:15:57,750 --> 00:16:00,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've looked up to him 
since I was a child.</font>

157
00:16:01,340 --> 00:16:04,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone in the city wants those memoirs.</font>

158
00:16:04,550 --> 00:16:06,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like you to find them.</font>

159
00:16:07,560 --> 00:16:09,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Himmel's memoirs...</font>

160
00:16:09,940 --> 00:16:11,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come to think of it,</font>

161
00:16:11,900 --> 00:16:15,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he said he'd lost the memoirs 
he'd been working on during our travels.</font>

162
00:16:16,170 --> 00:16:17,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was pretty disappointed, I think.</font>

163
00:16:21,840 --> 00:16:24,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe that's where they were.</font>

164
00:16:25,620 --> 00:16:28,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, we'll take the job.</font>

165
00:16:52,230 --> 00:16:56,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that a whole fleet of ships? 
It's like we're out at sea.</font>

166
00:16:56,100 --> 00:17:01,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. Many people and shipments of goods 
traverse the lake this time of year.</font>

167
00:17:02,060 --> 00:17:04,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And lately, there have been 
rumors that a Golden Land,</font>

168
00:17:04,560 --> 00:17:09,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">where anything and everything is made 
of gold, was found in the north.</font>

169
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:13,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">More people are crossing 
the lake than usual.</font>

170
00:17:13,250 --> 00:17:16,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Golden Land? Is that true?</font>

171
00:17:16,640 --> 00:17:18,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knows?</font>

172
00:17:18,860 --> 00:17:22,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I've never met anyone 
who's actually been there.</font>

173
00:17:23,230 --> 00:17:25,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's probably just a tall tale.</font>

174
00:17:28,470 --> 00:17:29,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the island.</font>

175
00:17:42,940 --> 00:17:45,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The barrier isn't very strong.</font>

176
00:17:45,980 --> 00:17:49,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it seems to be several decades old.</font>

177
00:17:49,030 --> 00:17:53,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a grand monastery. 
Why was it abandoned?</font>

178
00:17:53,950 --> 00:17:57,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The roof caved in after a monster attack.</font>

179
00:17:57,610 --> 00:17:59,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was an old building.</font>

180
00:18:00,180 --> 00:18:04,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. That's why they erected 
the barrier in a hurry.</font>

181
00:18:05,060 --> 00:18:06,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

182
00:18:06,440 --> 00:18:11,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Most monasteries keep 
old and valuable books.</font>

183
00:18:12,020 --> 00:18:13,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh.</font>

184
00:18:14,120 --> 00:18:18,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So the barrier was for protecting the 
books they couldn't take with them.</font>

185
00:18:21,590 --> 00:18:24,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's open. Let's search the monastery.</font>

186
00:18:27,850 --> 00:18:30,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened to the monks who were here?</font>

187
00:18:31,440 --> 00:18:35,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who knows? It was abandoned 
a long time ago.</font>

188
00:18:35,340 --> 00:18:40,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The only knowledge that remains is the 
story about Himmel the Hero's memoirs.</font>

189
00:18:50,560 --> 00:18:52,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a big library.</font>

190
00:18:53,310 --> 00:18:55,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a statue of Mr. Himmel.</font>

191
00:18:56,350 --> 00:18:58,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a handsome pose.</font>

192
00:19:06,910 --> 00:19:08,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here we are.</font>

193
00:19:08,700 --> 00:19:09,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is it.</font>

194
00:19:13,690 --> 00:19:16,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup. This is definitely it.</font>

195
00:19:16,090 --> 00:19:17,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is Himmel's handwriting.</font>

196
00:20:17,560 --> 00:20:19,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's written in it?</font>

197
00:20:21,190 --> 00:20:23,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the everyday minutiae 
of a ridiculous journey.</font>

198
00:20:27,140 --> 00:20:28,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just everyday stuff.</font>

199
00:20:31,230 --> 00:20:33,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here. This is what you asked for.</font>

200
00:20:34,220 --> 00:20:36,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now our fare is paid in full.</font>

201
00:20:39,530 --> 00:20:44,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I heard an elven mage traveled 
with the party of heroes,</font>

202
00:20:44,740 --> 00:20:46,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I never thought I'd get to meet her.</font>

203
00:20:47,440 --> 00:20:49,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What made you think it was me?</font>

204
00:20:49,770 --> 00:20:53,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After seeing that wistful look 
on your face, how could I not?</font>

205
00:20:53,840 --> 00:20:57,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's something important to you, 
isn't it? You should keep it.</font>

206
00:21:00,040 --> 00:21:04,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are plenty of other 
valuable books here.</font>

207
00:21:04,300 --> 00:21:06,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's more than enough payment.</font>

208
00:21:07,960 --> 00:21:10,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did it really show on my face?</font>

209
00:21:10,700 --> 00:21:11,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only a little.</font>

210
00:21:12,830 --> 00:21:16,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on. We'll reach the 
far shore before sunset.</font>

211
00:21:22,920 --> 00:21:26,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sure we'll need this 
collection of cool catchphrases.</font>

212
00:21:26,250 --> 00:21:27,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a waste of pages.</font>

213
00:21:27,990 --> 00:21:30,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I'll use one next time.</font>

214
00:21:30,010 --> 00:21:35,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Come at me, monster! I, Stark 
the warrior, shall take you on!"</font>

215
00:21:38,300 --> 00:21:39,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

216
00:21:40,140 --> 00:21:41,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a kraken!</font>

217
00:21:42,150 --> 00:21:44,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There are sea monsters here, too?!</font>

218
00:21:44,680 --> 00:21:46,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You provoked it.</font>

219
00:21:46,600 --> 00:21:47,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's <i>my</i> fault?!</font>

220
00:21:48,370 --> 00:21:52,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stark, if we don't defeat it quickly, 
it'll drag us all to a watery grave.</font>

221
00:21:54,070 --> 00:21:54,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ms. Frieren!</font>

222
00:21:54,780 --> 00:21:55,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Frieren!</font>

223
00:21:58,370 --> 00:22:00,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stark, this monster's weakness is—</font>

224
00:22:00,380 --> 00:22:01,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What?</font>

225
00:22:02,690 --> 00:22:05,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's how you two can now 
take it down. Good luck.</font>

226
00:22:06,410 --> 00:22:09,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ms. Frieren seems to be using 
the spell that allows you</font>

227
00:22:09,380 --> 00:22:12,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to say tongue twisters without 
tripping over your words.</font>

228
00:22:12,510 --> 00:22:13,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

229
00:22:14,160 --> 00:22:18,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are you two so calm? It's scary.</font>

230
00:22:20,980 --> 00:22:25,110
<font face="Times New Roman" size="12" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="10">Translation
<font size="12">Sho Stifler

