231
00:23:50,090 --> 00:23:52,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a 3,000 meter drop.</font>

232
00:23:50,710 --> 00:23:53,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}The risk matches the reward, huh?</font>

233
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:52,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's beautiful.</font>

234
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:53,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's reacting to our mana.</font>

235
00:23:53,760 --> 00:23:55,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we defeat the Demon King,</font>

236
00:23:55,830 --> 00:24:00,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a time will come when anyone 
can enjoy this beautiful sight.</font>

237
00:23:56,080 --> 00:24:00,070
<font face="Times New Roman" size="24">{\an8}<font color="#000000">Episode 38







A Beautiful Sight</font></font>

